<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.8">
<l>kāṇpārā remmīcaṉ kaṇṇaṉaiyeṉ kāṇumā</l>
<l>ṟūṇpēci lellā vulakumōr tuṟṟāṟṟā</l>
<l>cēṇpāla vīṭō vuyirōmaṟ ṟepporuṭku</l>
<l>mēṇpāluñ cōrāṉ parantuḷā ṉeṅkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who are those that will see my lord? Which way is there to see Kṛṣṇa?</l>
<l>If speaking of food, one rice [grain] will not assuage all the world.</l>
<l>Is there liberation or life for those whose fate it is to be distant? For everything</l>
<l>he who does not slip from the eight parts spreads [and] is everywhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
